Package: qgert
Type: Package
Title: Qualitas Genetic Evaluation Routine Tools
Version: 0.8.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Peter",
           family = "von Rohr",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "peter.vonrohr@qualitasag.ch")
Author: Peter von Rohr  [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Peter von Rohr <peter.vonrohr@qualitasag.ch>           
Description: Results of routine genetic evaluations are post-processed to generate different reports
    for quality assurance. The validity of the results of a given analysis is assessed by a comparison 
    to the results of a previous analysis. This package provides a number of tools for such comparisons.
